These incredible pictures show a lightning storm above the city of Houston, Texas, from a very unusual perspective - the edge of space.

The stills are from a Vime - a short Twitter video - posted by Nasa astronaut Reid Wiseman, 38, who is aboard the International Space Station in low earth orbit.

It shows the awesome power of a storm over the city from above and was posted on Friday. The rapid-fire flashes can be seen through the dense mass of clouds.

